original:
Once upon a time, there was a curious young boy named Timmy. One day, he saw his grandfather sitting under a tree, eating a juicy apple. Intrigued, Timmy approached his grandfather and said, "Grandpa, can you teach me how to eat an apple?"
Smiling, his grandfather agreed and took him to the orchard. As they walked, Timmy noticed how the trees swayed in the breeze, their leaves whispering secrets.

Smiling, his grandparent agreed and took him to the orchard. As they walked, Timmy noticed how the trees swayed in the breeze, their leaves whispering secrets.
